title: Café Noir
description: Hip coffee shop that roasts its own beans, sells pastries & sandwiches, & offers barista workshops.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How does this place compare to Mame and Coffee Shack?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Café Noir roast their own coffee and they do a very good job at this! I can recommend it for a quick but delightful coffee break. Mame is perfect for trying new coffee specialties and Coffee Shack is nice if you want more than "just" coffee.
